      "writtenOn": "2026-07-07T06:45:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The doc says the name is used \"for error messages\", but as far as I can tell it only ever surfaces in the export error (internal/core/export/value.go). None of the call-time errors reference it: the closure\u0027s NewErrf calls below (\"expected %d argument(s)\", \"decoding argument %d\", \"%v\") don\u0027t include cfg.name, and adt.Func.rawCall\u0027s incomplete-argument error uses call.Fun. So e.g. a 2-arg func named \"adder\" called with one arg still reports just \"expected 2 argument(s), got 1\", with no mention of \"adder\".\n\nTestNewPureFunc1Name sets a name but only asserts on the error text, so this gap isn\u0027t exercised. Could we either thread f.Name into these messages (matching how Builtin errors read \"in call to X\"), or narrow the doc comment to say the name is only used when exporting?",
      "revId": "33f6c190c4175be335aeb12ac77332e210cbc795",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": false,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "abf464e6_9b9f7b01",
        "filename": "cue/func.go",
        "patchSetId": 19
      },
      "lineNbr": 34,
      "author": {
        "id": 1007275
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-10T12:35:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Threaded the name into the call-time errors. Func.rawCall now wraps a *Bottom result as \"error in call to \u003cname\u003e\" with the call position, mirroring Builtin.rawCall (see the reply on expr.go). This covers all the closure errors (arg count, decoding, user error), so a 2-arg func named \"adder\" called with one arg now reports \"error in call to adder: expected 2 argument(s), got 1\". When no name is set it falls back to \"function\". TestNewPureFunc1Name now asserts the name appears in the message, so the gap is exercised. The doc comment is now accurate.",
      "parentUuid": "2295b079_7757f703",
      "revId": "33f6c190c4175be335aeb12ac77332e210cbc795",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "dabe39ee_df913a05",
        "filename": "cue/func.go",
        "patchSetId": 19
      },
      "lineNbr": 58,
